      <title>斯洛伐克总理菲佐表示不会屈服于民众压力而辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/slovak-premier-fico-says-won-t-bow-to-popular-pressure-and-quit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于四名联盟议员拒绝投票，除非他们的要求得到满足，斯洛伐克总理罗伯特·菲佐领导的政府面临失去议会多数席位的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/slovak-premier-fico-says-won-t-bow-to-popular-pressure-and-quit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 12:34:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
